cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.MM 

The paper deals with fashion recommendation and mapping of fashion items based on their attributes and sales data. This involves the use of deep neural networks to process image and tag data, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the use of machine learning models to predict sales, which falls under the machine learning (cs.LG) sub-category. Additionally, the paper involves natural language processing (cs.CL) in the form of tag data processing, and multimedia (cs.MM) in the form of image data processing.
